    Product Description

    Anxiety and mood issues are NOT all in your head... but they may be in your gut.

    Mood Boosting Probioticâ  is our original MOOD formulated probiotic featuring 9 feel-good strains of probiotic bacteria + prebiotic GOS; all designed to help with mood health, digestive health, and immune health.â 

    Recent studies have proven that adding beneficial bacteria to the gut can reduce anxiety and stress in the body.

    We've included the best bacterial strains to help with mood and aid the body's stress response.

    We created our MOOD probiotics because we believed there had to be a better way to feel better.

    Mood Boosting Probiotic Features

    • 30 Billion CFU
    • 9 Specific strains of targeted feel-good probiotic bacteria
    • Prebiotic GOS. The best prebiotic (fiber) for mood support
    • Shelf stable formula (No refrigeration required!)
    • Capsules you can OPEN to help you go slow with your dosage -- perfect for sensitive individuals
    • 60 day supply
    • Friendly, compassionate customer support.
    Read more

    We are Sylvia and Tim Hall

    The founders of Lifted Naturals. We are passionate about the gut-brain connection and we specialize in probiotics for MOOD.

    All Lifted Naturals probiotics are made in our FDA approved facility* which is GMP Certified. Our team is completely committed to safe and effective probiotics for mood and digestion.

    Whether you're looking for stress and anxiety relief, depression support, or digestive relief, our products can help.

    Read more

    Helpful Tips for Taking our Probiotic




    GO SLOW

    Our TOP-TIP for probiotic success is to GO SLOW with the dosage at first.â  â 

    Starting with as little as 1/4 or 1/8 of a capsule is a great way for sensitive individuals to get the full benefits our probiotics offer.

    Gas/bloating are often a signals that your body needs more probiotic bacteria, but it can be frustrating if those are the symptoms you are trying to get rid of by taking a probiotic!

    You can reduce the chance of having these issues by slowing down your dosageâ€¦

    â  Because our probiotics have no fillers or added ingredients, you can open the capsule and pour some of the ingredients into a smoothie, applesauce, or other food.

    â  Then slowly work your way up to a full capsule.

    BE CONSISTENT

    Be sure to take your probiotic every day for best results.

    We recommend taking it with a meal, which helps the good bacteria get where it needs to go.

    Some people swear our probiotics make them sleepy and so they take them at night.

    Others swear they are energized by them and so they take them every morning with breakfast.

    It really requires a personal â€˜trial and error' based on what your body needs.

    Consistently taking our probiotic helps to ensure the most benefit!

    HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE?

    For some individuals, the mood benefits kick in fairly quickly.

    For others it can take a full bottle.

    We always try to remind customers that it has taken years of microbiome damage to cause an imbalance and it can take a while to regain proper balance of good bacteria.

    Oftentimes, the digestive benefits will happen first with the mood benefits coming on more gradually.

    Probiotics are not one-size-fits-all. We are happy to help with questions regarding which MOOD formulated probiotic might be best for you.

First I'm going to list some issues I've had that are relevant to my situation, and then fill it in with backstory.

      -=Symptoms beforehand=-
      * Constant Anxiety for no apparent reason. -always worried, no idea why. No major life change to worry about
      * Horrible nightmares that would come out of nowhere. (extremely realistic)
      * Stool was always soft and greasy
      * unable to sleep all night
      * Brain fog/confusion
      * odd lightheaded feeling that I can't explain in words
      * heart palpitations
      * unbelievable amounts of fatigue
      * no joy in doing ANYTHING, couldn't even get into TV
      * constant acid reflux, especially bad at night.

      -=Symptoms afterwards=-
      * Anxiety stopped in under a week of taking these two times a day
      * First few days I had stomach upset but it subsided fairly quickly
      * no more acid reflux after two weeks.
      * No more nightmares.
      * finally able to sleep an entire night
      * minimal fatigue to none now. (getting better every day, almost at a month)
      * brain fog has gotten much better
      * heart palpitations have almost completely gone away.
      * finally living and enjoying life again
      * Stool is more regular and no greasy.

      Small backstory:
      I'm sensitive to specific strains of Pro-biotics. I didn't always know this, but over the past few years its become apparent. My problem started after being on Nutrisystem shakes that contain a probiootic. (I didnt know it at the time but I created my problem because of this. Also found that "white pearls" effect me as well. After being on "normal" probiotics I eventually got a constant nervous feeling of impending doom which eventually turned into worrying about family, death, etc. not great stuff. I was constantly nostalgic and wishing I was back when times were good. (not that times aren't now, but I felt bad for so long I felt like this was what life was going to be like for now on) I had no idea why I had fallen into this feeling, but every day and every night I had it, for over a year. I was absolutely miserable. My Dr. tried to put me on Lexipro. -Biggest mistake for me ever. It compounded my issue ten fold, gave me insomnia, etc. I stopped the pills after a week due to not even being able to function at work. I never got back to baseline after that. Its the closest I've ever felt to insanity. When that didn't work he suggested I talk to a psychiatrist. I knew deep down this had to be a medical condition and not some underlying stress thing but didn't know what to do. I was alone with nobody to help. After much reading online I found information about what happens when you gut bacteria is off and how that effects well being. From there I found a group forum talking about many different similar issues I was having and they all recommended this product. I decided to purchase it and give it a try. (mostly because of the reviews) I couldn't believe that after a few days of starting this probiotic, finally, after over a YEAR of anxiety, I finally started to find relief. After a few days I had actually slept all night and was shocked.

      Truth be told, I'm pretty upset at the three Dr's I've gone to with NONE of them even suggesting a probitoic like this. In retrospect I don't even believe at this point they took me seriously because I didn't want to be on an SSRI. (basically it was my fault for feeling this way because I don't want to be on medication) Further When I discussed how my stomach was always upset and how fatigued I'd get after eating even small meals, it was suggested I just try other meals. Unbelievable.

      At anyway rate, if you've made it this far in this wall -o- text of a review, I'd implore ANYONE who has any of these symptoms to at least give this an honest try for a week. It has saved me in ways I can't even begin to explain. I keep a bottle at work and a bottle at home. That was I always have them for lunch and dinner.

      I Hope this helps even one person make the leap. I know not everything works for everyone, but this has changed my life and finally fixed the issues I was having. Stay well everyone!

My mood is lighter and I'm just happier in general.
